::Spears::

She felt his arms slide around her waist and her back.  She felt her 
lips press against his.  She closed her eyes and felt her spark jump. 
SHe felt him press against her. She could believe he was kissing her 
back.  She liked it.  She felt he was worth risking her spark for.  
And his kiss was most  deffinantly worth it.  

She opened her eyes as he leaned back. She smiled and sighed.  she 
closed her eyes as he kissed her again.  Sher spark raced and her 
head reeled.  She was in the matrix right at that moment.
